nodes.documentation:
@title SafeMath
Math operations with safety checks that revert on error
nodes.name: SafeMath

nodes.documentation: Multiplies two numbers, reverts on overflow.
nodes.name: mul

nodes.documentation: Integer division of two numbers truncating the quotient, reverts on division by zero.
nodes.name: div

nodes.documentation: Subtracts two numbers, reverts on overflow (i.e. if subtrahend is greater than minuend).
nodes.name: sub

nodes.documentation: Adds two numbers, reverts on overflow.
nodes.name: add

nodes.documentation:
@dev Divides two numbers and returns the remainder (unsigned integer modulo),
reverts when dividing by zero.
nodes.name: mod
